--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Project Structure--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        frontend/
 ├─ public/                   
 │   ├─ index.html
 │   └─ favicon.ico
 ├─ src/
 │   ├─ assets/                # Images, icons, static files
 │   │   ├─ images/
 │   │   └─ icons/
 │   ├─ components/            # Reusable UI components
 │   │   ├─ Navbar.jsx
 │   │   ├─ Footer.jsx
 │   │   ├─ MovieCard.jsx
 │   │   ├─ Seat.jsx
 │   │   └─ BannerSlider.jsx
 │   ├─ pages/                 # Full pages mapped to routes
 │   │   ├─ Home.jsx
 │   │   ├─ MovieDetails.jsx
 │   │   ├─ Booking.jsx
 │   │   ├─ Payment.jsx
 │   │   └─ Profile.jsx
 │   ├─ redux/                 # Global state management
 │   │   ├─ store.js
 │   │   ├─ userSlice.js
 │   │   └─ bookingSlice.js
 │   ├─ services/              # API calls
 │   │   ├─ authService.js
 │   │   ├─ movieService.js
 │   │   └─ bookingService.js
 │   ├─ hooks/                 # Custom React hooks
 │   │   └─ useAuth.js
 │   ├─ utils/                 # Helper functions
 │   │   └─ formatDate.js
 │   ├─ styles/                # CSS files
 │   │   ├─ App.css
 │   │   └─ components.css
 │   ├─ App.jsx
 │   └─ index.jsx
 └─ package.json
 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Project Structure--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        backend/
 ├─ config/                      # Configuration files
 │   ├─ database.js             # MongoDB connection
 │   └─ jwt.js                  # JWT configuration
 ├─ controllers/                # Request handlers
 │   ├─ authController.js       # Authentication logic
 │   ├─ movieController.js      # Movie operations
 │   ├─ bookingController.js    # Booking operations
 │   ├─ userController.js       # User operations
 │   └─ paymentController.js    # Payment processing
 ├─ models/                     # Database models
 │   ├─ User.js                 # User schema
 │   ├─ Movie.js                # Movie schema
 │   ├─ Show.js                 # Show schema
 │   ├─ Booking.js              # Booking schema
 │   ├─ Theater.js              # Theater schema
 │   └─ Seat.js                 # Seat schema
 ├─ routes/                     # API routes
 │   ├─ authRoutes.js           # Authentication routes
 │   ├─ movieRoutes.js          # Movie routes
 │   ├─ bookingRoutes.js        # Booking routes
 │   ├─ userRoutes.js           # User routes
 │   └─ paymentRoutes.js        # Payment routes
 ├─ middleware/                 # Custom middleware
 │   ├─ auth.js                 # JWT authentication
 │   ├─ errorHandler.js         # Error handling
 │   └─ validation.js           # Input validation
 ├─ utils/                      # Utility functions
 │   ├─ generateToken.js        # JWT token generation
 │   ├─ sendEmail.js            # Email utilities
 │   └─ helpers.js              # Helper functions
 ├─ .env                        # Environment variables
 ├─ .gitignore                  # Git ignore file
 ├─ server.js                   # Main server file
 └─ package.json                # Dependencies



User
-------------------
City -- #location
 └── Theatre -- #cinema hall
      └── Screen -- #individual screens inside a theatre
           └── Show -- #movies alocated tot the theater
                └── Seat-- #physical seats layout
                     └── ShowSeat -- #seat status (available / booked / blocked)
                             └── Booking -- #final booking record

